 are ao, a;, di, bh, and cg. Bug-killers appear as an 
 huge function since bug-killers are applied in 
 eastern China according to certain conditions (e.g. 
 pest (situations where large numbers of harmful or disgusting things exist)), but bug-killer use levels off rather 
